al studies.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 4aLiterary Studies. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / General.2bisacsh1 aAdkins, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAlsen, Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlomvall, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCullen, Lauren, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCurry, Elizabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEckersley, Karen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFagan, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoldman, Jane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoody, Alex, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoody, Alex, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHovanec, Caroline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJarzębowska, Gabriela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcCracken, Saskia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMurray, Rachel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPandey, Beerendra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRohman, Carrie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRyan, Derek, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeil, Kari, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWu, Juanjuan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEdinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z97831107976400 cprintz978147449802